title: Coming back to rust 5k hours lfg
selftext: Hello, I am coming back to rust after a few months break. I am looking for a group of people who know what to do and know who to play. I am 19, and I am pretty chill and like to have fun but also get stuff done in the wipe. My discord is banna#4797 add me if you are looking for another member for your team.
